r/Juan Chen","line":125},{"title":"Author/Juan Chen","target":"Author/Juan Chen","line":126},{"title":"Author/Shunxing Guo","target":"Author/Shunxing Guo","line":127},{"title":"Author/Shunxing Guo","target":"Author/Shunxing Guo","line":128},{"title":"Author/Juanjuan Ren","target":"Author/Juanjuan Ren","line":129},{"title":"Author/Jinwei Ren","target":"Author/Jinwei Ren","line":130},{"title":"Author/Jinwei Ren","target":"Author/Jinwei Ren","line":131},{"title":"Author/Wenzhao Wang","target":"Author/Wenzhao Wang","line":132},{"title":"Author/Wenzhao Wang","target":"Author/Wenzhao Wang","line":133},{"title":"Author/Yong Tao","target":"Author/Yong Tao","line":134},{"title":"Author/Yong Tao","target":"Author/Yong Tao","line":135},{"title":"Author/Yong Tao","target":"Author/Yong Tao","line":136},{"title":"Author/Wen-Bing Yin","target":"Author/Wen-Bing Yin","line":137},{"title":"Author/Wen-Bing Yin","target":"Author/Wen-Bing Yin","line":138},{"title":"Author/Hongwei Liu","target":"Author/Hongwei Liu","line":139},{"title":"Author/Hongwei Liu","target":"Author/Hongwei Liu","line":140},{"title":"PDF","target":"biblib/yang_discovery_2017/yang_discovery_2017.pdf","line":142}],"metadata":{"id":"yang_discovery_2017","type":"article-journal","title":"Discovery and Characterization of a New Family of Diterpene Cyclases in Bacteria and Fungi","issued":{"date-parts":[[2017]]},"DOI":"10.1002/anie.201700565","container-title":"Angewandte Chemie","abstract":"Diterpene cyclases from bacteria and basidiomycete fungi are seldom studied. Here, we presented the identification and verification of EriG, a member of the UbiA superfamily, as the enzyme responsible for the cyclization of the cyathane skeleton in the mushroom Hericium erinaceum. Genome mining using the EriG protein sequence as a probe led to the discovery of a new family of ubiquitous UbiA-related diterpene cyclases in bacteria and fungi. We successfully characterized seven new diterpene cyclases from bacteria or basidiomycete fungi with the help of an engineered Escherichia coli strain and determined the structures of their corresponding products. A new diterpene with an unusual skeleton was generated during this process. The discovery of this new family of diterpene cyclases provides new insight into the UbiA superfamily.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Yang","given":"Yanlong","literal":""},{"family":"Yang","given":"Yan-Long","literal":""},{"family":"Zhang","given":"Shasha","literal":""},{"family":"Zhang","given":"Shasha","literal":""},{"family":"Zhang","given":"Shasha","literal":""},{"family":"Ma","given":"Ke","literal":""},{"family":"Ma","given":"Ke","literal":""},{"family":"Xu","given":"Yuxing","literal":""},{"family":"Xu","given":"Yuxing","literal":""},{"family":"Tao","given":"Qiaoqiao","literal":""},{"family":"Tao","given":"Qiao-Qiao","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Yihua","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Yihua","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Yihua","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Juan","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Juan","literal":""},{"family":"Guo","given":"Shunxing","literal":""},{"family":"Guo","given":"Shunxing","literal":""},{"family":"Ren","given":"Juanjuan","literal":""},{"family":"Ren","given":"Jinwei","literal":""},{"family":"Ren","given":"Jinwei","literal":""},{"family":"Wang","given":"Wenzhao","literal":""},{"family":"Wang","given":"Wenzhao","literal":""},{"family":"Tao","given":"Yong","literal":""},{"family":"Tao","given":"Yong","literal":""},{"family":"Tao","given":"Yong","literal":""},{"family":"Yin","given":"Wen-Bing","literal":""},{"family":"Yin","given":"Wen-Bing","literal":""},{"family":"Liu","given":"Hongwei","literal":""},{"family":"Liu","given":"Hongwei","literal":""}],"citation-key":"yang_discovery_2017","year":"2017","dateCreated":"2026-03-31","reading-status":"to-read","aliases":["Discovery and Characterization of a New Family of Diterpene Cyclases in Bacteria and Fungi"],"author-links":["[[Author/Ya